properties.name: jwt.expiration.refresh
properties.description: Token expiration time in milliseconds. Default 1 day (86400)

properties.name: websocket.message-size-limit
properties.description: Maximum size in Kb of the HTTP post or put request body. Default is 64KB

properties.name: jwt.secret
properties.description: the signing key used to verify any discovered JWS digital signature. If the specified JWT string is not a JWS (no signature), this key is not used

properties.name: web.config.cors.allowedOrigins
properties.description: List of urls that are allowed to access the resources.

properties.name: websocket.send-time-limit
properties.description: Set the maximum time (in seconds) that a message is allowed to be processed by the server. Default is 10 seconds

properties.name: websocket.send-buffer-size-limit
properties.description: Maximum size in Kb of the HTTP post or put request body. The default value is 512K

properties.name: file.limit-file-count-upload
properties.description: Specifies the maximum number of files that can be uploaded

properties.name: file.limit-file-size-upload
properties.description: Maximum file size (in MB) that allow to upload. The default value is 10(MB)

properties.name: file.path-upload
properties.description: Location to save the uploaded file

properties.name: application.title
properties.description: Application title displayed on the banner console

properties.name: application.version
properties.description: Application version displayed on the banner console

properties.name: file.limit-avatar-size-upload
properties.description: Maximum file size (in MB) that allow to upload. The default value is 10(MB)
